&lt;li&gt;Providing support to customers who are experiencing network related issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responding to and troubleshooting alerts as well as participating in our on-call rotation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rolling out new network infrastructure to our various locations remotely around the world&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimizing our automation and monitoring&amp;nbsp; systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
